<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Bon de livraison {{ order.name }}</title>
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 16mm 14mm; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Jost', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #121212;
    font-size: 11pt;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .brand, h1, h2 {
    font-family: 'Prata', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  header.doc-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #121212;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .brand {
    font-size: 22pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .brand-tagline {
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #B08D57;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .doc-title {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .doc-title h1 {
    font-size: 15pt;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }
  .doc-title .order-number {
    font-size: 13pt;
    color: #B08D57;
  }
  .doc-title .order-date {
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #555;
  }
  .meta-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .meta-block { flex: 1; }
  .meta-block h2 {
    font-size: 10pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #B08D57;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .meta-block p { margin: 0; font-size: 10.5pt; }
  table.line-items {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  table.line-items thead th {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 9pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #B08D57;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #121212;
    padding: 8px 6px;
  }
  table.line-items tbody td {
    padding: 10px 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
  }
  table.line-items td.qty,
  table.line-items td.price,
  table.line-items td.total,
  table.line-items th.qty,
  table.line-items th.price,
  table.line-items th.total {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .item-cell { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .item-cell img {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
  }
  .item-cell .placeholder-swatch {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: #121212;
  }
  .item-title { font-weight: 500; }
  .item-sku { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #777; }
  .totals {
    width: 260px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .totals .row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 4px 0;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
  }
  .totals .row.total {
    border-top: 1px solid #121212;
    margin-top: 6px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12pt;
    font-family: 'Prata', Georgia, serif;
  }
  .note-block {
    background: #F3F3F3;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
  }
  .note-block h2 {
    font-size: 9pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #B08D57;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid #121212;
    padding-top: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  footer .thanks {
    font-family: 'Prata', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 12pt;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  footer .legal {
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #777;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="doc-header">
  <div>
    <div class="brand">Diva by Diane</div>
    <div class="brand-tagline">Be a diva</div>
  </div>
  <div class="doc-title">
    <h1>Bon de livraison</h1>
    <div class="order-number">{{ order.name }}</div>
    <div class="order-date">{{ order.created_at | date: '%d/%m/%Y' }}</div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="meta-grid">
  <div class="meta-block">
    <h2>Expédier à</h2>
    {% if order.shipping_address %}
      <p>
        {{ order.shipping_address.name }}<br>
        {{ order.shipping_address.address1 }}<br>
        {% if order.shipping_address.address2 %}{{ order.shipping_address.address2 }}<br>{% endif %}
        {{ order.shipping_address.zip }} {{ order.shipping_address.city }}<br>
        {{ order.shipping_address.country }}
        {% if order.shipping_address.phone %}<br>{{ order.shipping_address.phone }}{% endif %}
      </p>
    {% else %}
      <p>Retrait en boutique / adresse non renseignée</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <div class="meta-block">
    <h2>Détails commande</h2>
    <p>
      N° commande : {{ order.name }}<br>
      Date : {{ order.created_at | date: '%d/%m/%Y' }}<br>
      {% if order.email %}Email : {{ order.email }}<br>{% endif %}
      {% if order.phone %}Tél : {{ order.phone }}{% endif %}
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<table class="line-items">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Article</th>
      <th class="qty">Qté</th>
      <th class="price">Prix unit.</th>
      <th class="total">Total</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for line_item in order.line_items %}
      <tr>
        <td>
          <div class="item-cell">
            {% if line_item.image %}
              <img src="{{ line_item.image | image_url: width: 96 }}" alt="{{ line_item.title | escape }}" width="48" height="48">
            {% else %}
              <div class="placeholder-swatch"></div>
            {% endif %}
            <div>
              <div class="item-title">{{ line_item.title }}</div>
              {% if line_item.sku != blank %}<div class="item-sku">Réf. {{ line_item.sku }}</div>{% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td class="qty">{{ line_item.quantity }}</td>
        <td class="price">{{ line_item.final_price | money }}</td>
        <td class="total">{{ line_item.final_line_price | money }}</td>
      </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="totals">
  <div class="row">
    <span>Sous-total</span>
    <span>{{ order.subtotal_price | money }}</span>
  </div>
  {% if order.total_discounts and order.total_discounts != 0 %}
    <div class="row">
      <span>Remise</span>
      <span>-{{ order.total_discounts | money }}</span>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
  <div class="row">
    <span>Livraison</span>
    <span>{% if order.shipping_price and order.shipping_price != 0 %}{{ order.shipping_price | money }}{% else %}Offerte{% endif %}</span>
  </div>
  {% if order.tax_price and order.tax_price != 0 %}
    <div class="row">
      <span>TVA</span>
      <span>{{ order.tax_price | money }}</span>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
  <div class="row total">
    <span>Total</span>
    <span>{{ order.total_price | money }}</span>
  </div>
</div>

{% if order.note %}
  <div class="note-block">
    <h2>Note de la cliente</h2>
    <p>{{ order.note }}</p>
  </div>
{% endif %}

<div class="note-block">
  <h2>Conseil d'entretien</h2>
  <p>
    Pour préserver l'éclat de votre bijou, évitez le contact prolongé avec l'eau,
    les parfums et les produits cosmétiques. Rangez-le à l'abri de l'humidité
    lorsque vous ne le portez pas.
  </p>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="thanks">Merci d'avoir choisi Diva by Diane</div>
  <div>Suivez-nous : @divabydiane</div>
  <div class="legal">
    Retour possible sous 14 jours à compter de la réception, frais de retour à
    la charge de la cliente. Voir notre politique de retour sur divabydiane.fr.
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
